post.description:
重排模型测试接口,对文档进行相关性排序

使用示例:
```bash
curl -X POST "http://localhost:8080/api/v1/console/model_test/rerank/test" \
  -H "Authorization: Bearer YOUR_TOKEN" \
  -H "Content-Type: application/json" \
  -d '{
    "provider": "Cohere",
    "name": "rerank-multilingual-v3.0",
    "query": "什么是人工智能?",
    "documents": [
      "人工智能是计算机科学的一个分支",
      "机器学习是人工智能的子领域",
      "深度学习使用神经网络"
    ],
    "top_n": 3
  }'
```

响应示例:
```json
{
  "code": 0,
  "message": "success",
  "data": {
    "results": [
      {
        "index": 0,
        "document": "人工智能是计算机科学的一个分支",
        "score": 0.95
      },
      {
        "index": 1,
        "document": "机器学习是人工智能的子领域",
        "score": 0.87
      }
    ],
    "total_results": 2
  }
}
```

